  <section class="grid">
    <article class="card"><h3>Starter</h3><p>Perfect for exploring Auto Video. Limited video renders per month, community support.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Team</h3><p>Brand presets, shared prompt workspace, campaign templates, and priority support.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Enterprise</h3><p>Custom pipeline design, dedicated support, private deployment options, and advanced analytics.</p></article>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
